EventItemActionText: A motion was made that this Land Use Call-Up be Approved, by Council approved by Roll Call.
EventItemTitle:
By The Chair of the Land Use Committee (Council Member Salamanca, Jr.)
Pursuant to Sections 11.20(b-d) of the Council Rules and Section 197-d(b)(3) of the New York City Charter, the Council hereby resolves that the actions of the City Planning Commission on related Application No. C 200083 PQK  (1510 Broadway) shall be subject to Council review.  This item is related to Application Nos. N 200082 ZRK, C 200085 ZMK, and C 200084 HAK.
EventItemMatterName: Zoning, 1510 Broadway, Brooklyn (C 200083 PQK, N 200082 ZRK, C 200085 ZMK and C 200084 HAK)
